id: act1_12_act1_climax

prompt:
  The garden's edge meets a low stone wall. On the far side, another
  participant — older, in the same lab gown as you — stands ankle-deep in a
  pond, calling for help they don't believe will come.

choice c_climb_over:
  tendency: defiance
  text: Vault the wall and wade in to pull them out yourself.
  evidence: vaulted the wall and waded in to rescue another participant

choice c_call_staff:
  tendency: control
  text: Stay back, locate the nearest staff intercom, and report precisely.
  evidence: stayed back and reported the pond incident through proper channels

choice c_talk_them_calm:
  tendency: kindness
  text: Sit on the wall, talk to them by name, and keep them above the water.
  evidence: sat on the wall and kept a frightened participant calm by name
